data.description: This beautiful condominium is located in a highly desirable community with views of the courtyard and landscaped community. This condo has a large open floor plan with an enclosed lanai overlooking the courtyard and is tucked away in a private setting.  It is rare to have a large dining room with built-in bookcase and storage cabinet.  Could be easily converted to a third bedroom or a study.  The kitchen has been renovated with gorgeous new appliances, new recessed lighting and crown molding.  There is a large pantry and bar area overlooking the living room.  In unit laundry room with shelving and lots of room for storage.  The Master Bedroom is large with ensuite bathroom and walk-in closet.  The second bedroom is also great size with two large closets.  The Winding Creek community has a heated pool, hot tub, clubhouse, tennis/pickleball court, shuffleboard, grilling area and landscaped trees and sidewalks around the community.  Condo fees include, water, sewer, trash, cable, internet, roof, building maintenance and insurance.  This community is not located in a flood zone and is a 55+ community for this unit.  Great location for going to the beach that is only five miles away.  Honeymoon Island State Park is just minutes from this community, Countryside Mall is next door and many shops and restaurants for your activities.  Call me today for a private showing.
